title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 05.13.08
description:
YOU&#039;RE THE RAPIST

Time for Change? At the young age of 15, Shichaela&#039;s already been raped, abused, addicted to drugs, and even prostituted for money. She attributes her downward spiral to her neglectful and abusive mother, Michelle, who never showed Michelle any love. Michelle wants a change in her life, but before Steve can help her, she needs to help herself. Will she make the right decision, and will she finally be able to confront her mother?
